---
title: Steak and Fennel-Apple-Walnut Salad with Creamy Caramelized Onion Gravy and Smashed Potatoes
description: It's steak night and we're setting you up with a dinner that's sure to impress! We've elevated delicious pan-seared steak with a creamy caramelized onion gravy. The steak isn't the only star though! Smashed potatoes and a special occasion salad with fennel, apples and walnuts come alongside.
